00:13:05.88 --> 00:13:10.88
Another thing he did, he orchestrated a raid

249
00:13:10.88 --> 00:13:15.88
on a POW camp called O'Flog 13B.

250
00:13:17.08 --> 00:13:18.16
It was impolent.

251
00:13:18.16 --> 00:13:21.12
And there's, I'm not going to go into the details now,

252
00:13:21.12 --> 00:13:23.80
but he actually thought that perhaps his son-in-law

253
00:13:23.80 --> 00:13:24.92
was a prisoner there.

254
00:13:24.92 --> 00:13:29.92
And so he organized this raid and a guy named Abraham Baum,

255
00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:36.08
conducted the raid, 300 men went on the mission,

256
00:13:36.08 --> 00:13:40.60
of which 32 were confirmed killed in action

257
00:13:40.60 --> 00:13:45.60
and another 200 over 200 were missing or taken prisoner

258
00:13:45.76 --> 00:13:50.28
and only 35 of the 300 made it back to friendly lines.

259
00:13:50.28 --> 00:13:52.48
So that is not good.

260
00:13:52.48 --> 00:13:56.000
And then on top of that, here's where I look at

261
00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:59.24
and I say if he would have had more humility.

